        description: 'List expenses.\n\nRetrieve a list of expenses using the @apideck/mcp-native package. You can specify filters to narrow down the results. The operation returns an array of expense records matching the criteria.\n\nRead-only; safe to call repeatedly.\n\nRequires an active `accounting` connection on the consumer\'s Apideck Vault. If the tool returns a connection error, use URL elicitation to guide the consumer to reconnect.',
